  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1d17a8d1204c5a840badf223e84742a6, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "\u2026And then it turned out, third guy brought his girlfriend. So
    I\u2019m pretty certain both of them were consenting, but me & BFF totally did
    not consent to seeing that, it was pretty explicit\u2026 Never thought we\u2019d
    have to add that clause to the set of rules for reenactment funsies, but both
    me and BFF agreed that we\u2019re not banning girls. Would it just be easier
    if we banned the third guy instead?"
